{"tid":2119222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美眾院表決大比數通過　聯邦及國會公務機禁用TikTok","createTime":"2020-07-22T03:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T18:58:12.000Z","uid":28114,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e6007dd71b20dfbc99fdf43fc97199686e973c1a","tid":2119222,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/us-ban-07212020051054.html/us-ban.png/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fus-ban-07212020051054.html%2Fus-ban.png%2F&h=07e99f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院通過投票，禁止聯邦公務員用公務機下載中國影音軟件TikTok。另外，除了聯邦僱員外，國會議員和員工也受此法規範。<br />\n<br />\n是項提案由共和黨眾議員巴克（Ken Buck）提出，是作為《國防授權法案》修正案的一部分，已於當地時間周一（20日）以336票同意、71票反對通過。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院將在周二（21日）對眾院版本的《國防授權法案》進行總體投票。稍後，參議院也將在本周就參議院版本進行表決，兩院分別通過之後將在聯合協調委員會中就法案分歧處協商。<br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》則報道，目前特朗普政府正在辯論如何阻止中國從TikTok等社交平台獲取美國公民個人資料；報道引述3名熟知特朗普團隊討論的消息來源指出，其中一個被討論的選項是把字節跳動列入貿易黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/us-ban-07212020051054.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fus-ban-07212020051054.html&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=85e00984\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/us-ban-07212020051054.html</a>"},{"pid":"e74a8870d9a95f0cc693cddbe8ebc116e361f4c9","tid":2119222,"uid":39200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"竟然唔禁埋微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab7ba19944e09f7e61dca335819b98c44c9d5de","tid":2119222,"uid":180851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:47:00.000Z","msg":"前期唔係話班後生為左佢暴動咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c790f1d919314cf3ae4155c5b79b958d590c6d","tid":2119222,"uid":132405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:48:50